# Backend Experiments

Name: Aman Raj
UID: 24BCF10016
Section: 24BCF-1(B)

## Description
This project demonstrates:
1. CLI Employee Management (CRUD operations)
2. REST API for playing cards
3. Ticket booking system with concurrency control

## Features
- Add/delete employees
- Fetch card data
- Seat booking with locking

## Technologies
HTML, CSS, JavaScript

## Conclusion
This project simulates backend concepts including CRUD operations, REST APIs, and concurrency handling.
